description:
using stack.sh install cloud environment, nova-novncproxy failed to start, the error showed:
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "/opt/stack/nova/bin/nova-novncproxy", line 80, in <module>
    server = console.websocketproxy.NovaWebSocketProxy(
AttributeError: 'module' object has no attribute 'websocketproxy'

test on the latest nova/commit f24cfa8093913466658a3ce2d9dc907c0c813239
title: nova-novncproxy failed to start due to no attribute 'websocketproxy'
